Class TectonHttpSinkConnectorConfig

java.lang.Object
org.apache.kafka.common.config.AbstractConfig
com.tecton.kafka.connect.TectonHttpSinkConnectorConfig
public class TectonHttpSinkConnectorConfig extends org.apache.kafka.common.config.AbstractConfig
Configuration class for TectonHttpSinkConnector. Holds the configuration parameters required to sink data to the Tecton Ingest API.
